## CLI

```bash
my docs setup
my docs list
my docs generate
my docs generate --only architecture,security
my docs generate --force
```

## Safety

Existing docs are **not** overwritten unless `--force` is provided.

## Usage

```ts
import { registerDocumentation } from './src/documentation/index.js';

const docs = registerDocumentation();
console.log(docs.list());
console.log(docs.plan());
```
